.TH "libnvmf_connect_ctrl" 9 "libnvmf_connect_ctrl" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvmf_connect_ctrl \- Connect a controller
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" libnvmf_connect_ctrl
.BI "(libnvme_ctrl_t c "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "c" 12
Controller to be connected
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Issues a 'connect' command to the NVMe-oF controller.
\fIc\fP must be initialized and not connected to the topology.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, or an error code on failure.
